<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ title }} - TOUTLUX</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #007bff 0%, #0056b3 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 26px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .notification-type {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .type-info { background-color: #cfe2ff; color: #084298; }
        .type-success { background-color: #d1e7dd; color: #0f5132; }
        .type-warning { background-color: #fff3cd; color: #664d03; }
        .type-danger { background-color: #f8d7da; color: #842029; }
        .main-content {
            margin: 20px 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }
        .highlight-box {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #007bff;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .button-success { background-color: #28a745; }
        .button-warning { background-color: #ffc107; color: #212529; }
        .button-danger { background-color: #dc3545; }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .icon-inline {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            vertical-align: middle;
            margin-right: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="email-container">
    <div class="header">
        <h1>{{ icon|default('üîî')|raw }} {{ title }}</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        {% if type %}
            <span class="notification-type type-{{ type }}">
                    {{ typeLabel|default(type|upper) }}
                </span>
        {% endif %}

        <p>
            Bonjour {{ user.firstName }},
        </p>

        <div class="main-content">
            {{ message|raw }}
        </div>

        {% if highlights %}
            <div class="highlight-box">
                {% for highlight in highlights %}
                    <p style="margin: 5px 0;">
                        <strong>{{ highlight.label }} :</strong> {{ highlight.value }}
                    </p>
                {% endfor %}
            </div>
        {% endif %}

        {% if actionUrl %}
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{ actionUrl }}" class="button button-{{ actionType|default('primary') }}">
                    {{ actionText|default('Voir plus') }}
                </a>
            </div>
        {% endif %}

        {% if additionalInfo %}
            <div style="margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;">
                {{ additionalInfo|raw }}
            </div>
        {% endif %}

        <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px;">
            Vous recevez cette notification car vous √™tes inscrit sur TOUTLUX avec l'email {{ user.email }}.
            Vous pouvez g√©rer vos pr√©f√©rences de notification dans vos
            <a href="{{ url('app_settings_notifications') }}" style="color: #007bff;">param√®tres</a>.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>
            ¬© {{ 'now'|date('Y') }} TOUTLUX - Tous droits r√©serv√©s<br>
            <a href="{{ url('app_privacy') }}" style="color: #666666;">Politique de confidentialit√©</a> |
            <a href="{{ url('app_terms') }}" style="color: #666666;">Conditions d'utilisation</a>
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 12px; margin-top: 20px;">
            Pour vous d√©sabonner de ce type de notification,
            <a href="{{ url('app_unsubscribe', {'token': unsubscribeToken, 'type': notificationType}) }}" style="color: #666666;">
                cliquez ici
            </a>.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
